title: Franchise/Transition Tag Reaction - Dak Prescott, Derrick Henry, A.J. Green & More, Kirk Cousins signs extension (Football 3/16)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to react to the franchise tag deadline and the massive list of players that were tagged this year (3:30). The guys discuss Dak Prescott, Derrick Henry, A.J. Green, Hunter Henry, Joe Thuney, Kenyan Drake, Shaq Barrett, Chris Jones, Leonard Williams, Matt Judon, Yannick Ngakoue, Brandon Scherff, Justin Simmons, Bud Dupree and Anthony Harris. Then, the Pick Six Superfriends analyze the 2-year extension that the Vikings signed Kirk Cousins to on Monday morning (38:30).

'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Castbox, Bullhorn and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
